            "animation_duration": 0.5,
            "animation_easing": "ease",
            "item_1_title": "Why Marame Exists",
            "item_1_content": "<span style=\"text-transform:none !important;\">\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    Marame was born out of years of personal frustration trying to build a wardrobe around core, timeless pieces that actually worked together.\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    Not just in style, but in fit, colour, quality, and wearability.\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    I spent years searching for staple items that felt great to wear, looked effortless, and could be styled in multiple ways for different occasions. I wanted flattering shapes, classic cuts, complementary colours, and fabrics that felt soft, substantial, and high quality. Clothes that looked as good the tenth time as they did the first.\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    What I couldn’t find was one brand I could rely on. One place where every piece felt considered and interchangeable. So, driven by that frustration and a love of a challenge, I pulled together a team who shared the same standards and decided to create it.\n  </span>\n\n</span>",
            "item_2_title": "The Marame Approach",
            "item_2_content": "<span style=\"text-transform:none !important;\">\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    Marame is built around the idea of a purposeful wardrobe.\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    We design pieces that make getting dressed easier, not harder. Clothes that don’t rely on trends to feel relevant. Staples you can mix, match, and re-style without second-guessing.\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    Every garment is designed to be an option. Something you reach for instinctively because it fits well, feels right, and works with what you already own. The kind of piece that earns its place in your wardrobe and stays there.\n  </span>\n\n</span>",
            "item_3_title": "Built With Intention",
            "item_3_content": "<span style=\"text-transform:none !important;\">\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    Every Marame piece is designed with intention, made to last, and produced responsibly.\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    We think carefully about fabric, fit, finish, and how each garment feels to wear and live in. From how a fabric drapes and softens over time, to how a seam sits or a neckline falls, nothing is accidental.\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    We work closely with trusted production partners who share our commitment to quality, ethical manufacturing, and responsible practices. These are not decisions we take lightly, and we would rather take longer or say no than compromise.\n  </span>\n\n</span>",
            "item_4_title": "The Journey So Far",
            "item_4_content": "<span style=\"text-transform:none !important;\">\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    Creating Marame has been a two-and-a-half-year journey defined by obsessive detail and determination.\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    We researched fabrics from mills around the world, compared swatches under different light, tested weights and textures, and rejected anything that didn’t meet our standards. We said no a lot. To materials that looked good but didn’t wear well. To suppliers who couldn’t guarantee quality or ethics. To finishes that didn’t feel quite right.\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    Patterns were drafted, redrafted, and tested across different body types. Small details were refined again and again. At one point, a single design went through more than 40 iterations. We even laboured over the exact weight of a button.\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    It was slow, intense, and at times exhausting. But it mattered.\n  </span>\n\n</span>",
            "item_5_title": "What Comes Next",
            "item_5_content": "<span style=\"text-transform:none !important;\">\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    If you’ve ever felt uninspired by your wardrobe, or frustrated by clothes that only work for a moment, Marame was made for you.\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    This brand is about building something long-lasting. Pieces you trust. A wardrobe that works harder so you don’t have to.\n  </span>\n  <br><br>\n\n  <span style=\"font-size:0.9em;\">\n    This is just the beginning, and we’re incredibly glad to have you with us.\n  </span>\n\n</span>",
